Step 1: Create New ECR Reposity
Step 2: Copy the Image Name and create a AWS Batch '462435663755.dkr.ecr.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/hit-data-dev'
Step 3: Create New Compute Environment in AWS Batch. For simplicity, I created On-demand env
Step 4: Create New Job Queues based on this compute env

Create Docker Image and deploy to AWS

Step 1: Build Docker image by executing this command from Terminal
		docker build -t <image_name> .
Step 2: Login to AWS ECR via terminal 
		aws ecr get-login-password --region us-east-1 --no-verify-ssl
Step 3: docker login --username AWS --password <image_name>
Step 3: Push the image by executing this command
		docker push <image name>
